resumes.text: Experienced Python developer with 5 years of experience in web development, machine learning, and data analysis. Proficient in Django, Flask, and scikit-learn.
Senior Software Engineer with 8 years of experience in Java development, Spring Framework, and microservices architecture.
Data Scientist with 3 years of experience in Python, pandas, and scikit-learn. Strong background in statistical analysis and machine learning.
Frontend Developer with 4 years of experience in React, JavaScript, and CSS. No backend or Python experience.

job_descriptions: Looking for a Python developer with experience in web development and machine learning. Must have strong knowledge of Django/Flask and data analysis.
Senior Java Developer position requiring extensive experience with Spring Framework and microservices.
Data Scientist position requiring Python, pandas, and machine learning experience.
Frontend Developer position focusing on React and modern JavaScript frameworks.
